Introduction

Precious Daughters was a South Korean girl group. They debuted on December 22, 2021 with the single "Sweep". The song was written, composed and arranged by the members alone. The members have over 10 years experience in the music industry previously.

They are presumed to have disbanded silently some time shortly after debut.
